metronome base generator (genesis "base" king)
================================================

This generator vendors and adapts a subset of the synthetic time-series
generators from the TempoPFN project. The vendored code lives under
``tempo_gen/`` and is import-rewritten (``src.*`` -> ``tempo_gen.*``) but is
otherwise derived from the upstream sources.

